\id JON  
\h Jona 
\toc1 Jonah 
\toc2 Jona 
\toc3 Jona 
\mt1 Jona  
\c 1  
\s1 Jona i botewayatho Giya Loi ghal…®Ňčae  
\p
\v 1 Va mbaŇča regha \nd Giya Loi\nd* ghal…®Ňčae i mena weya Jona Amitai nariye.  
\v 2 I dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúU yondovir…® Jona, na e ghembako lagh…®ye Ninive e t…®ne, u dage weŇčgi lenji thar…® i lagh…®ye moli na tene ya mukuwoŇčgi.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 3 Ko iyemaeŇčge Jona i voiteta \nd Giya Loi\nd* na ma i wareriŇčava ghemba regha idae Tasis. I wareri na i wa Jopa, na gheko ve vaidiya waŇčga regha kaero ghambaŇča vara i wareri Tasis kaiwae. Jona i wa ve vamodo waŇčgako, kaero i thawe na i wa Tasis kaiwae i munjeva i voiteta \nd Giya Loi\nd*. \fig Jona i wa ve vamodo waŇčgako, kaero i thawe na i wa Tasis|src="co01409B.tif" size="col" copy="DCC" ref="1:3" \fig*   
\p
\v 4 Amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* i variya ndewendewe vur…®vur…®ghegheniye regha na i nja weŇčgi e gh…®nagha mborowa. Ndewendeweko le vur…®gheghe kaiwae waŇčgako vama ina vara e thar…® t…®ne.  
\v 5 Gharelagh…®lagh…® kaiwae waŇčgako gharakakaiwo regha na regha tembe i goyawaru weya le loi thalavu kaiwae. Lenji renuwaŇča th…® munjeva th…® vamayaŇča waŇčgako e vuyowoko t…®ne, th…® mbana doweko vavana th…® yathu e njigh…®ko t…®ne.  
\p Ko iyemaeŇčge e mbaŇčako iyako Jona vambe ina e waŇčgako ghar…®ghe, e t…®ne bode i ghenetena yawaliye.  
\v 6 WaŇčgako ghakap…®tan i nja na ve vaidi na i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúKo iya ŇčgoroŇčga mbe len ghenaeŇčge e waŇčgako t…®ne? U thuweiru na wo u naŇčgo weya len loi. Mbwata ne ghare i nja weinda na ma val…®kaiwae raya mare.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 7 WaŇčgako gharakakaiwo th…® vedage weŇčgi th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúWo ra tamwe thela le thar…® kaiwae iya ra vaidiya vuyowoke iyake. Wo ra vakatha bigi regha Ňčgoreiye sula.‚ÄĚ\f + \fr 1:7 \ft Kaiwae nuwanjiya th…® ghareghare thela me vakatha ghanji vuyowo, th…® vakatha bigi regha Ňčgoreiye sula. Th…® vakatha ghar…®ghar…® ghanjinono e var…®var…® nanasiye vwatanji regha na regha. Amba th…® mban…®thuwole e nambo t…®ne na lolo regha na i tuthiya var…® regha. Ma i thuwe. Var…®ko iyako loloko me vakatha ghanji vuyowoko ghanono inawe. E kamwath…®ko iyako ghar…®ghar…® th…® loŇčweghath…® Loi i vatomwe weŇčgi thela i vakatha ghanji vuyowo. VaŇča lumo raŇča ‚Äúcasting lots‚ÄĚ. \f* MbaŇča th…® vakatha iyako ve nja weya Jona.   
\p
\v 8 Iya kaiwae th…® vaito th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúE mbaŇčake iyake wo u utu giyama weime, thela le thar…® kaiwae na iya vuyowoke iyake i yomara weinda? U vakatha budakai gheke? The vanautuma loloniya ghen? The wabwi loloniya ghen?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 9 I gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúHibru loloniya ghino na ya kururu weya \nd Giya Loi\nd*, Loi ina e buruburu, iye va i vakatha njigh…® na thelau.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 10 WaŇčgako gharakakaiwo th…® gharelagh…®lagh…® lagh…®ye moli na th…® dagewe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúBudakaiya iya mo vakathake?‚ÄĚ (Th…® ghareghare mendava i vo weya \nd Giya Loi\nd* kaiwae me utu giya weŇčgi.)   
\p
\v 11 Lenji utuutuko e t…®ne ndewendeweko ma i vur…®gheghe na i vur…®gheghe eŇčge. Iya kaiwae th…® vaito th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúNe wo vakatha budakai e ghen na mbala ndewendeweko i rowo towo na ghime yawal…®me?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 12 Jona i gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúHu woŇčgo na hu duutuŇčgo e njigh…®ke t…®ne, ambane tad i ghagha. Ya ghareghare ghino kaiwaŇčgu iya hu vaidiya vuyowoke iyake.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 13 IyemaeŇčge waŇčgako gharakakaiwo th…® wodo na th…® munjeva th…® goru vanat…®na ‚ÄĒ th…® rovur…®gheghe lagh…®ye moli, ko iyemaeŇčge ndewendeweko vama i vur…®gheghe eŇčge na vanat…®na ma i bwagabwaga moli eŇčge weŇčgi.  
\v 14 Iya kaiwae th…® goyawaru weya Jona le Loi th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúAee \nd Giya Loi\nd*, wo naŇčgo e ghen thava ne u lith…® e ghime e mare kaiwae ne wo vakowana loloke iya ma ghawonjoweke yawaliye. Ghen mbe ghan…®mbereghana vara iya len renuwaŇča vakathake thiyake th…® yomara.‚ÄĚ  
\v 15 Th…® wovaira Jona e n…®man…®manji na th…® wokiyathuutu e njigh…®ko t…®ne. E mbaŇčako iyako tad i ghagha.  
\v 16 Iyako i vathaŇčgiya waŇčgako gharakakaiwo th…® mararu lagh…®ye moli weya \nd Giya Loi\nd* iya kaiwae th…® vakatha vowo na i vorowe na th…® vakatha Ňčgoreiye lenji dagerawe.   
\p
\v 17 Ko iyemaeŇčge Jona kaiwae, \nd Giya Loi\nd* i vivatharawa borogi lagh…®ye regha na i wovoŇčgwa Jona. Jona va ina e borogiko Ňčgamoiye ghararagh…®ye thegheto na gougou gheneto.   
\c 2  
\s1 Jona le naŇčgo  
\p
\v 1 Maya borogiko e Ňčgamoiye t…®ne, Jona i naŇčgo weya \nd Giya Loi\nd* le Loi.  
\v 2 IŇča:  
\q1 ‚ÄúMbaŇča inaŇčgu vuyowo lagh…®ye e t…®ne,  
\q2 na ya una \nd Giya Loi\nd* idan,  
\q3 kaero u thalavuŇčgo.  
\q1 Bode moli ramaremare e ghambanji,  
\q2 ya una idan thalavu kaiwae,  
\q3 na u loŇčwa ghal…®ŇčaŇčgu.   
\q1
\v 3 U duutuŇčgo e Ňčambuwoko t…®ne bode moli,  
\q2 njigh…® i vagh…®liyaŇčgo,  
\q2 len bagodu lagh…®lagh…®ye th…® bebe e vwataŇčgu.   
\q1
\v 4 Lo renuwaŇča yaŇčaeŇčge kaero mendava u kiten…®yathuŇčgo e ghen  
\q2 ko tembene ya thuweva len Ňägolo Boboma.   
\q1
\v 5 Mbwa i wovululuŇčgo na i wovoŇčguŇčgo;  
\q2 na njigh…® i garubu riwaŇčguke lagh…®ye,  
\q2 na njigh…®ko wolewaniye i ghavwa umbal…®Ňčgu.   
\q1
\v 6 Ya nja e Ňčambuwokote e ououko r…®gher…®ghenji  
\q2 e val…®vaŇčgake iya ghath…®n…®mbako  
\q3 ma mbaŇča regha i mavu.  
\q1 Ko iyemaeŇčge ghen, wo \nd Giya Loi\nd*, lo Loi,  
\q2 u vaŇčgunjoghaŇčgo e yawayawaliŇčgu  
\q3 bode moli e Ňčambuwoko t…®ne.   
\q1
\v 7 MbaŇča ya gham…®no yawaliŇčgu kaero ne iko,  
\q2 amba ya renuwaŇčakikiŇčge na ya naŇčgo e ghen, o \nd Giya Loi\nd*  
\q2 na e len Ňägolo Bobomana e t…®ne u loŇčwa ghal…®ŇčaŇčgu.   
\q1
\v 8 Thavala th…® goru weya vatavatad…®Ňčgi  
\q3 na ma e ghanji thovuye,  
\q2 kaero th…® roiteteŇčge na  
\q3 gharen ma i nja weŇčgi.   
\q1
\v 9 Ko iyemaeŇčge ne ya wothu taraweŇčge;  
\q2 ne ya vakatha vowo na i voro e ghen  
\q2 na ya vakatha Ňčgoreiya va lo dagerawe e ghen.  
\q2 Vamoru i mena weya \nd Giya Loi\nd*!‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 10 Amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* i vakatha borogima na i thegharaŇčgiya Jona e njigh…®ko ghadidiye.   
\c 3  
\s1 Jona i wa Ninive  
\p
\v 1 Amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* mbaŇčaiwoniyeva i dage weva Jona,  
\v 2 iŇča, ‚ÄúU wa Ninive, iya ghembako lagh…®ye iyako na vo utuŇča totoke iya ya utuveŇčgeke.‚ÄĚ \fig Jona i ghambugha Giya Loi le renuwaŇča na i wa Ninive, iya ghembako lagh…®ye iyako|src="co01417b.TIF" size="col" copy="DCC" ref="3:2" \fig*   
\p
\v 3 Jona i ghambugha \nd Giya Loi\nd* le renuwaŇča na i wa Ninive, iya ghembako lagh…®ye iyako. I wo mbaŇča thegheto amba lolo regha i loŇčga e t…®ne na ve wo val…®ghadidiye.  
\v 4 MbaŇča i viva moli i Ňčgalauwa e ghembako lagh…®ye t…®ne. I utuŇča iŇča, ‚ÄúNe mbaŇča mbaŇčaevar…® e t…®ne Ninive ne i mukuwo moli.‚ÄĚ  
\v 5 Ninive ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® loŇčweghath…®gha Loi le utu iya Jona me utugiya weŇčgi, iya kaiwae th…®Ňča val…®kaiwae ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye th…® mbemba, iri thavala th…® lagh…®ye na th…® mevoro gheghad ghar…®ghar…® ma e idaidanji na th…® njimbo kwama mbe ghayamoyamo Ňčgoreiye ela le gh…®moru i mareiteteŇča, na iyako i woraŇčgiya kaero th…® roiteteŇčgiya lenji thar…® na th…® ndeghereiye wanaŇčgi. \fig Jona i utuŇča iŇča, ‚ÄúNe mbaŇča mbaŇčaevar…® e t…®ne Ninive ne i mukuwo moli.‚ÄĚ|src="co01420b.TIF" size="col" copy="DCC" ref="3:4" \fig*   
\p
\v 6 MbaŇča ghembako ghakiŇč i loŇčwa iyako, i yondovir…® ele ghamba mbaroko weiye vwenyevwenye kwamaniye na i linjoŇča ghakwamako amba i liya kwama Ňčgoreiye wambwi kwamaniye na ve ronja e vugha vwatae.  
\v 7 Amba i variya ghal…®Ňčae weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye Ninive e t…®ne iŇča,  
\pmc ‚ÄúKiŇč na ghal…®Ňčae gharaghamb…® th…® variya utuke iyake weŇčga, Ňčgoreiyake:  
\pm Thava lolo regha, thava kau, sip na gout th…® ghan…®Ňčga o th…® muna mbwa.  
\v 8 Ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye na thetheghan th…® njimbo kwama ghanjiyamoyamo Ňčgoreiye wambwi kwamaniye. Ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye th…® naŇčgo vur…®gheghe weiye lenji gharevatomwe weya Loi, na th…® roiteteŇčgiya ghanjithanavu raraithar…® na lenji vakatha raraithar…®.  
\v 9 Mbwatane Loi i v…®va le renuwaŇča na le ghareghaith…®ko iko, ghare i nja weinda na mbala ma i mukuwoinda.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 10 MbaŇča Loi i thuwa lenji vakathako, kaero th…® roiteteŇčgi ghanjithanavu raraithar…®, i v…®va le renuwaŇča na le ghareghaith…®ko iko na ma i mukuwoŇčgi Ňčgoreiya va iŇča ne i vakatha weŇčgi.   
\c 4  
\s1 Jona le ghatemuru na Loi le mwaewo  
\p
\v 1 Ko iyemaeŇčge Jona va weiye le ghatemuru lagh…®ye moli iyako kaiwae weiye le gaith…®.  
\v 2 Iya kaiwae i naŇčgo weya \nd Giya Loi\nd* iŇča, ‚Äú\nd Giya Loi\nd*, amba muyai ya iteta ghambaŇčgu, thare va ya dage e ghen na len vakatha Ňčgoreiye vara iyako? Iyako kaiwae va ya rovur…®ghegheŇča na ya vogha na ya wa Tasis (Spein). Ya ghareghare ghen gharethovu na mwaewo gha Loi. MbaŇčake wolagh…®ye u ghataŇčaghath…®, mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye gharen…®we, na mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye val…®kaiwan u v…®va len renuwaŇča na ma giya vuyowo.  
\v 3 Iya kaiwae, \nd Giya Loi\nd*, mbema u li eŇčge yawaliŇčguke, val…®kaiwae moliya ya mare na thava e yawayawaliŇčgu.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 4 Ko iyemaeŇčge \nd Giya Loi\nd* i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúMa e len r…®ghe na iya gharen…®na i gaith…®.‚ÄĚ \fig Giya Loi i vakatha umbwa regha i mbuthu voro Jona evasiwae|src="co01422b.TIF" size="col" copy="DCC" ref="4:6" \fig*   
\p
\v 5 Jona i wareri na i wa e ghembako val…®vaŇčga e boimako na ve yakuwe. I vatada yoŇčathowathowa regha na i yaku e riburibuye, na i roroghagha; nuwaiya i thuwe budakai ne i yomara e ghembako iyako.  
\v 6 Amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* i vakatha umbwa regha i mbuthu voro Jona evasiwae na i giya ghambaghambaluwae na i vakatha gham…®nae i thovuye moli. Jona i warari lagh…®ye umbwako iyako kaiwae.  
\v 7 Ko va mbaŇčambaŇčava moli Loi iŇča na mwatamwata th…® ghana umbwama na i mare.  
\v 8 Varae vama i yovoro na e ghereiye Loi i vakatha boima dayadayaghaniye i rowo na i vakatha Jona mbalavama marae i tatailo kaiwae varaeko va i Ňčge umbaliye na i dayagha. Iya kaiwae iŇča, ‚ÄúThoŇčgo mbema ya mare eŇčge. Val…®kaiwae moliya ya mare na thava e yawayawaliŇčgu.‚ÄĚ \fig Val…®kaiwae moliya ya mare na thava e yawayawaliŇčgu|src="co01423b.TIF" size="col" copy="DCC" ref="4:8" \fig*   
\p
\v 9 Ko iyemaeŇčge Loi i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúMa e len r…®ghe vara na gharen i gaith…® umbwako kaiwae.‚ÄĚ  
\p Jona i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúMbe elo r…®ghe na kaiwae ghareŇčgu i gaith…® ‚ÄĒ ya gaith…® lagh…®ye lagh…®ye moli iya kaiwae nuwaŇčguiya mbema ya mare vara.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 10 Ko iyemaeŇčge \nd Giya Loi\nd* i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúIya umbwako menda i mbuthuko na gougoura na kaero i mareva, ma menda u vakatha bigi reghawe na ma menda u vakatha na i mbuthu, iwaeŇčge gharen i njawe.  
\v 11 ŇägoroŇčga na mbe ghareŇčgu wevara iya ghembako lagh…®ye Ninive. Kaiwae e t…®ne ghar…®ghar…® lenji ghanaghanagha i kivwala wan handred tuwen…®ti tausan ghar…®ghar…® ma val…®kaiwanji th…® ghareghare thovuye na thar…® inanjiwe, na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva thetheghan…®Ňčgi lemoyo.‚ÄĚ   